This project is the landing page for https://www.innpilot.ai.

It is built with Astro, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS, then deployed as a static
Cloudflare Worker asset bundle.

## Commands

```sh
pnpm install
pnpm dev
pnpm build
pnpm deploy
```

`pnpm build` runs `astro check` before generating the static site into `dist/`.
`pnpm deploy` builds the site and publishes `dist/` using Wrangler.

## GitHub Actions Deployment

The workflow in `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` runs on pull requests to `main`,
pushes to `main`, and manual dispatches. Pull requests build the site. Pushes to
`main` and manual dispatches build the site, then deploy it to Cloudflare
Workers with Wrangler.

Add these repository secrets in GitHub before deploying:

- `CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID`: the Cloudflare account that owns the Worker.
- `CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN`: an API token with permission to edit Cloudflare
  Workers for that account.
